  dialogueLines:
  - Another piece. Is your hobby tearing up instructions?
  - It was a safety measure
  - (loud creak)
  - " I wasn\u2019t talking to you"
  - "The house?\u2026 I think it likes me"
  - " It does that when it thinks someone might be smarter than me \u2014 and starts
    helping"
  - "The house doesn\u2019t react to me anymore. Maybe it decided I already messed
    everything up"
  - (makes a sound)
  - She agrees too
  - "\u2026Traitor"
  dialogueManager: {fileID: 991258583}
  playOnlyOnce: 1
